org.lenskit.data.dao

Class PrefetchingUserDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lenskit.data.dao.PrefetchingUserDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Describable, UserDAO

    public final class PrefetchingUserDAO
extends Object
implements UserDAO, Describable

    User DAO that streams the events to get user information. The user set is fetched and memorized once for each instance of this class.

    2.0
